    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName> vende a <persName><name
                                ref="Ansegisus">Ansighisi</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Teudegisus">Teudighisi</name></persName> un appezzamento di
                        terra posto in loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/156">Canpo
                            Vitallani</placeName> ubi <placeName ref="#places/156"
                            >Valiano</placeName> vocatur, <rs key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >confinante</rs> da oriente con terra di <persName><name
                                ref="Isalbertus">Isalberto</name></persName>, da aquilone et
                        occidente con terra di <persName><name ref="Teudegrimus"
                            >Teudelgrimo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Teudegrimus"
                                >Teudelgrimo</name></persName>, da meridie via publica decurrente,
                        della misura per longo di 19 pertiche, per extraverso di 6 pertiche, per il
                        prezzo di 20 soldi d’argento. Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary"
                            >notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Walbrandus"
                            >Walprando</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum ad loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/155">Cornio</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness"
                            >Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name
                                ref="Wideradus">Witterado</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Adroaldus">Atrualdo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ursus">Orso</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Willeradus">Willerado</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>MDL, 5/2, n. 1000, p. 618; ChLA 86, n. 44, pp. 134-136.</p>
            </div>
